 | url=https://spectrumcomputing.co.uk/page.php?issue_id=1533&page=46
 | access-date=28 January 2023
 | issn = 0261-3697 }}
</ref>  Their common quest is to pursue the evil wizard Drax, who has fled to his dungeon hideout after his defeat in the first game. The player characters battle their way through an inhospitable wasteland, a system of caves, and a dungeon before facing Drax in his inner sanctum for a showdown.<ref name=dragon150>{{cite journal
