Using a joystick or keyboard, the player moves his or her character through ''Barbarian II''{{'}}s world. Each of the four stages&mdash;wasteland, caves, dungeon, and inner sanctum&mdash;is a series of interconnected rooms, populated by monsters, traps, and items.<ref name=dragon150 /> The game displays one room at a time in a [[flip-screen|flick-screen]] manner: as the protagonist leaves a room, the screen is updated to display the next.<ref name=zzap67>{{cite journal
