 | publisher = Croftward
 | location = United Kingdom
 | issn = 0955-1077 }}
</ref> A compass at the bottom of the interface serves as a directional guide, always pointing to the north.<ref name=ys32>{{cite journal
 | last = Nash
 | first = Tommy
 |date=August 1988
 | title = YS Megapreview&mdash;Barbarian II
